    "Consequently, there is a pressing need for regulators who perform the same role as the law enforcement authorities in the actual world, since it is anticipated that relevant laws and rules (such as real-name verification) would have to be put in place.",
    "As suggested by Zhang et al. (2022), traceability of creations, content, and works in the metaverse requires the employment of technologies such as blockchain and non-fungible tokens (NFT).",
    "If this does not happen, the metaverse may become a lawless environment, thus unsafe for students and instructors.",
    "An expanded TAM model was developed in this paper to investigate the main factors affecting higher education students' behavioral intentions to adopt metaverse technology in their education.",
    "Based on 574 questionnaire responses collected from higher education students at five universities in Jordan, perceived usefulness, personal innovativeness in IT, and perceived enjoyment had substantial direct positive effects on students' behavioral intentions."
